New Invocable Actions in Life Sciences Cloud

Use the new invocable actions in Participant Management to set up the randomization process for generating research study block records and assigning candidates to research study comparison groups.

Generate research study randomization block records: Use the generateResearchStudyBlocks action.
Randomly assign candidates to research study comparison groups: Use the assignCndtToResearchStudyGroup action.
